# AI prompt handling

- Do not change existing safety/disclaimer behavior accidentally.
- When editing Chat personas:
  - keep the language requirement (VN) and the “not legal advice” guidance.
  - keep the “ask up to 3 clarifying questions when missing data” guideline.
- Prefer extracting prompt constants into `src/lib/ai/*` as the app grows.

